<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-B240EAE5-F36D-4762-8DCF-692A8F3BCB4A" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-B240EAE5-F36D-4762-8DCF-692A8F3BCB4A" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">How to update a license via ORS</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="M148553-B105"><p class="- topic/p "> This document describes the installation of an update of a license. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> It is preferred that the customer does this himself, the procedure is also described in the operation guide. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> The actions are executed via the Settings Editor. This means that in case it needs to be done by a technician it can be done remotely via a teamviewer session. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-E5E04D2F-4497-4DCD-B2CB-C916A0B4B787" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The system is connected to ORS. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The customer has ordered additional licenses. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The customer is informed by the sales or service representative that the license change has been performed in the back office systems. 
</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="GUID-2B0B8AB8-E0D5-454C-A761-86ADFD3B9C65" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Install the license</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-733DF7DD-F449-4FB2-A48B-47D68D23353E" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" align="left" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" align="left" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="90*" align="left" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Wait approximately 5 minutes after having made the license request. 
</p><note id="GUID-BCD0B8A4-749E-4C7D-A2C0-397B4A7BE041" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> You can speed up the procedure by clicking on "Test remote connection" button in Remote Services section on operator panel. 
</p></note><p class="- topic/p "> There is no notification on the successful reception of the license. 
</p></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Go to the Settings Editor; Support --&gt; Licenses --&gt; Licenses, and click on "Install license from remote server". 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The following window appears: 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C45C31F-5F9B-4BA0-9224-D34FA6C88346" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Example</title><image href="GUID-B0CE3A0F-B22E-4D22-96D5-C3E55B941A58-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B0CE3A0F-B22E-4D22-96D5-C3E55B941A58-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Click on "Install", a warning "Restart" window will appear to warn that a Printer restart will be required to take into account the license, click on "OK" in this window: 
</p><fig id="GUID-625EC986-236A-457F-935D-8B2EAABBC054" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Example</title><image href="GUID-DEFA0148-7C4A-49E0-A500-335CFD47CD5C-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DEFA0148-7C4A-49E0-A500-335CFD47CD5C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> A successful message will appear to confirm the license has been successfully installed. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7CBEC1E2-FAD0-43F0-9E23-C96FCE716142" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Example</title><image href="GUID-3B633AD8-B65A-4BDC-8C54-187952298505-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3B633AD8-B65A-4BDC-8C54-187952298505-low.png"/></fig><note id="GUID-23E79F60-7A45-4436-A91A-2D1C59D1BD6F" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> The popup "restart the printer ... " does not result in a restart. This is a known issue. 
</p></note><note id="GUID-15966DD7-432D-462E-8D43-8D89F59742C4" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> When the error appears "An unknown error has occurred", probably the license is not yet available on the system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Retry again after 5 minutes. Not filling out the product license will also result in this error. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See 
<xref keyref="00GENDIAG_ORS" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-831E43AD-1571-4EDD-9EF4-77BC0E2AF128.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to diagnose a license retrieval error when requesting the license from...?>How to diagnose a license retrieval error when requesting the license from ORS</xref>. 
</p></note></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Click OK in this window. Then restart the printer via the menu Support --&gt;Troubleshooting --&gt; Printer restart and job removal --&gt; Restart the system. 
</p><fig id="GUID-08D63DB6-46A2-4B7D-9567-09E5389FE78B" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Example</title><image href="GUID-29CE2D45-26F9-4D4E-94B1-25E00322B3FD-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-29CE2D45-26F9-4D4E-94B1-25E00322B3FD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> After Restart, check the license(s) with the Settings Editor, Support --&gt; Licenses --&gt; Licenses: 
</p><fig id="GUID-94B9F3DE-2387-4BDC-90E4-A57607DE0AE6" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Example</title><image href="GUID-BBAD438A-2559-4490-B99E-EEFE37347D7B-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BBAD438A-2559-4490-B99E-EEFE37347D7B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-910D2375-F14D-4AF8-B3CB-33B59DACD534" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Troubleshooting</title><p class="- topic/p "> See 
<xref keyref="00GENDIAG_ORS" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-831E43AD-1571-4EDD-9EF4-77BC0E2AF128.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to diagnose a license retrieval error when requesting the license from...?>How to diagnose a license retrieval error when requesting the license from ORS</xref>. 
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-7D3F358C-1AB9-4A5D-9B0E-C75D689F152E.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
